<!-- TEMPLATE PAGE -->

<div class="content-col clearfix">

    <!-- IMAGE FRAME DOESN'T CHANGE EXCEPT FOR BACKGROUND IMG -->
    <div class="frame-container clearfix">
        <div class="image-frame">
            <div class="stats-bar clearfix">
                <div class="stat-35">
                    Capt Log<br>
                    OT-00<span class="idSpan">{{items.captain_id}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-20 prof">
                    <img height="13px" src="/images/prof_icon.svg">
                    <span>{{items.proficiency_points}}</span>
                    <div class="stat-text hide-prof">Proficiency</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-20 scrap">
                    <img height="12px" src="/images/scrap_icon.svg">
                    <span>{{items.scrap_amount}}</span>
                    <div class="stat-text hide-scrap">Scrap</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-20 crew">
                    <img height="12px" src="/images/crew_icon.svg">
                    <span>{{items.crew_hp}}</span>
                    <div class="stat-text hide-crew">Crew</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="image-box" style="background-image: url('../images/storyimg/3_2.png');"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="frame-container clearfix">
        <div class="text-frame">
            <div class="text-title">
                Planet Class H
            </div>
            <div class="text-divide"></div>
            <div class="text-body">
                As you approach you see clearly this is a desert type planet. Harsh temperatures and violent sandstorms can make it difficult for human survival. The science department would love the opportunity to take an away team down for some more detailed readings, despite the danger. After making it down to the planet's surface you must pick a direction to explore.
            </div>
            <div class="text-divide"></div>

            <!-- CHANGE DATA-ATTRIBUTES FOR EACH CHOICE // CHANGE DATA-CHAP/DATA-PAGE TO THE NEXT PAGE (SAME FOR EACH BUTTON) -->
            <div data-scrap="-5" data-crew="-1" data-prof="-1" data-chap="3" data-page="3a" class="option-buttons">
                West
            </div>
            <div data-scrap="0" data-crew="0" data-prof="0" data-chap="3" data-page="4" class="option-buttons">
                North
            </div>
            <div data-scrap="0" data-crew="0" data-prof="0" data-chap="3" data-page="5" class="option-buttons">
                East
            </div>
            <div data-scrap="0" data-crew="0" data-prof="0" data-chap="3" data-page="6" class="option-buttons">
                South
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/choice_buttons.js"></script>